    "Then, the type of sample signals obtained from the dataset are shown in Fig. 3.",
    "For this evaluation, the University of Bonn dataset has been used to test the performance and efficiency of the filtering approach, feature extraction model, and optimization mechanism separately.",
    "Table 2 shows the Peak Signal to Noise Ratio (PSNR) and SD of the existing Blackman window and maximally flat filtering techniques.",
    "For the signals obtained from the Bonn dataset, the average SNR and SD values are estimated by implementing both existing and proposed approaches.",
    "Then, these results stated that the proposed FLHF approach provides the reduced average SNR and SD values by eliminating the noise based on the probability estimation using the rectangular format of mother wavelets."
